text: .@UPSHelp If my Alternate Delivery Location Preference in the settings of UPS My Choice is set to "Send all packages directly to my preferred UPS Access Point location without attempting delivery to my address" do I need to specify to deliver it there and not my actual address?

@UPSHelp I have this as my setting & never had a problem. Packages always went to my AP, which is below my apt.  A delivery on 9/4 was left @ the front door of my building (in NY!) as noted on the delivery slip & not my AP. It is missing & I'm told it is my fault & need to specify to AP
@madinarope Please DM your tracking number with your delivery address and we'll take a look at your situation. ^ZM https://t.co/wKJHDXWGRQ
